Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Kusakabe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you have solved the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you bring the recovered data from the computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't recover the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all a plan by the Special Crimes Unit to lure you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The planner Professor Odagiri left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...the research he was conducting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A system to upload the human brain into the network.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...and his actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said that he used to run into Banno a lot during his walks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They even met after he died, apparently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be impossible to meet Banno on a walk if he was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the Professor's walks were in the network world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...then it wouldn't be strange for you to notice him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how come you knew of Kyu's email, which was only sent to the Special Crimes members?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Roidmude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Kusakabe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I eliminated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He became aware of the Anima System, took the data \Nfrom the Professor's computer, and deleted the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusakabe did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We were watching his every move. And then came the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You contacted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to avoid the Anima System \Nbeing spread throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is why you pretended to be Kusakabe and tried to keep us away from the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusakabe Akira knew too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill an innocent man like Kusakabe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Shinnosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I will avenge my comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Start you engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}DRIVE: TYPE SPEED!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming along for the ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}SP-SP-SPEED!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, I do not intend to fight you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Banno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,, You intended to use the confusion of the Global Freeze a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...to borrow the Anima System to take control of the Professor's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could escape the network world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the Professor accidentally died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And your plan to capitalize on the Global Freeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...was crushed by the Global Freeze itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ironic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to all of you, this case was solved successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My deepest thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there still something missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are Kyu and Otta in the Special Crimes Unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyu was scouted for his work with computers and the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So Officer Otta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because he was in charge of the case a year ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why he came to the Special Crimes Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... that puts my mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing the truth also puts me at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally not at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You just used us to figure out \Nsomething you wanted to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This was just a test of your competence as police officers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting as suspiciously as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts,Shinnosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't hurt! You're a belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
