Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}START YOUR ENGINE!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}The rain stops, there's a break in the clouds{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:25.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}The blue sky's calling out to you{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:29.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Alright, it's almost time to head out{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:32.75,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}I don't need anyone else's advice{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.67,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}I've gotta trust my own instincts{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:40.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}It's high time I found my own way{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.93,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Fire Up, Ignition{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}The heavy pressure's on{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Slam the accelerator and power through{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:53.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Surprise, the whole world's got drive!\N{\fs30}(It's faster than ever){\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:58.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Feeling high like you're finally awake\N{\fs30}(Show me your Drivin'){\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:03.74,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Once you're on the road to destiny\N{\fs30}(Keep chasin' forever){\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:09.72,Accident,,0,600,220,,{\b1\i1\pos(385,516)}A C C I D E N T !{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:08.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}There's no way to go in reverse...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\b1}All we need is Drive!{\b0}